What can you do from the Insight Display on a c-Class BladeSystem enclosure?
A. Access the Health Summary of the enclosure.
B. Change IP addresses of iLO 2 on individual blades.
C. Power individual blades on or off.
D. Power the enclosure on or off.
Answer: A

B. BL46Xc
C. BL49Xc
D. BL68Xc
E. BL8XXc
F. BL2x220c

stack from the server processor to the NIC?
A. TOE
B. WOL
C. iSCSI
D. PXE
E. RDMA
Answer: A
